{"tid":230374,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"新手想玩返釣魚,請高手指導","createTime":"2017-05-05T10:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T13:43:22.000Z","uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"896462af10ce746f674ea19bd96cf0e24be77a23","tid":230374,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:09:42.000Z","msg":"冇約都4,5年啦,之前都係玩下手排仔<br />\n而家見得閒D都想玩返,但想試下買支竿玩下<br />\n想問下一支竿最平幾錢,邊到買好,同埋最基本有咩工具,你地釣果陣會唔會帶埋魚袋攞返去"},{"pid":"54b62437f9dd405ab70e6544a7382fb46b88e7ba","tid":230374,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:08:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb9594646cbebe71b83ebfaf19c2207526e83a91","tid":230374,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:20:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇約都4,5年啦,之前都係玩下手排仔<br />\n而家見得閒D都想玩返,但想試下買支竿玩下<br />\n想問下一支竿最平幾錢,邊到買好,同埋最基本有咩工具,你地釣果陣會唔會帶埋魚袋攞返去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最平幾十蚊都有，攪又幾十蚊都有<br />\n不過買好少少冇壞嘅<br />\n最基本咪一竿一攪一絲一鉛一鈎<br />\n<br />\n唔帶魚返去，又唔係等住開飯，為咗享樂啫"},{"pid":"ca10495302e2549f3d8461a0ad33814ac7616730","tid":230374,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇約都4,5年啦,之前都係玩下手排仔<br />\n而家見得閒D都想玩返,但想試下買支竿玩下<br />\n想問下一支竿最平幾錢,邊到買好,同埋最基本有咩工具,你地釣果陣會唔會帶埋魚袋攞返去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最平幾十蚊都有，攪又幾十蚊都有<br />\n不過買好少少冇壞嘅<br />\n最基本咪一竿一攪一絲一鉛一鈎<br />\n<br />\n唔帶魚返去，又唔係等住開飯，為咗享樂啫</blockquote><br />\n係咪有分筏仔,投竿,巴打覺得新手買邊隻好D?<br />\n攪係咪咩竿都岩上架?"},{"pid":"9b44c1035915c9ff54d4b572f37b968d18c4d275","tid":230374,"uid":109996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:27:14.000Z","msg":"不如你講我知你想玩咩釣法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6493db8cfceec118aa2191792fc3f9cc89d4bba9","tid":230374,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:31:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如你講我知你想玩咩釣法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起岸邊/河邊/碼頭釣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新手悠閒式釣法<br />\n即係唔會出海/去魚排釣果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7caf33fcc75333b0077b375456d3c3383eef90d7","tid":230374,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:38:26.000Z","msg":"筆直200蚊左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想問下邊度會平D,因為怕D專門釣具店會賣好貴"},{"pid":"12c5a9c2c957066130eaece48e08bce821c322a8","tid":230374,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>筆直200蚊左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想問下邊度會平D,因為怕D專門釣具店會賣好貴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n200蚊，你讀緊書？<br />\n不如玩返手排先啦，用竿又唔一定好好多，只係範圍大啲咁解，手感亦都冇手排咁好"},{"pid":"8864fae498f0095f2dfbf48198bf799d4341a1f1","tid":230374,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T11:57:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不如你講我知你想玩咩釣法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起岸邊/河邊/碼頭釣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新手悠閒式釣法<br />\n即係唔會出海/去魚排釣果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁樣真係手排夠晒，如果你真係想買竿不如玩住手排儲多少少先，買餌都要錢架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dd4cce5db0b5677288b4b7fbc25206f20383eb","tid":230374,"uid":109996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:43:22.000Z","msg":"如果你係長遠玩落去，建議你買返普通裝<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係玩手排算啦"}]}